{
  "stem": "13851.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Kielce there were killed 40 people from my-- from the camp when they came back to look for anybody who's alive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were killed in Kielce.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we ran to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we joined a kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kibbutz was in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- we went from my hometown by a train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The trains were running already at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was told that there was a lot of happened on trains.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Many of those-- it was with the guns-- civilians-- they were civilians, but they call themselves-- they were looking for the people that like us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So how-- I-- I didn't know that by that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, you were lucky that they didn't get you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because if you look Jewish, they would take you down and kill you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was after the war, coming home to my hometown where I was born, and was raised.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we-- we went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we run, both us-- we went to Warsaw, because we thought, a little town, a bigger city, maybe we could survive more people together.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we joined a kibbutz there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what was the kibbutz like?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The kibbutz was-- the kibbutz at the time was-- was just-- it was the only way to go is to Israel, to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time there was no Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was Palestine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it's the only place to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't stay in Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was no use to stay in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had been through hell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we, I mean, they don't even want you to be there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They wanted to kill the people in the-- in the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we wanna go to some country where we be able to live.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the only thing is going to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
